1. প্রথমে এটা ইনস্টল করতে হবে composer require laravel/passport
error ashle
PHP → php.ini
;extension=sodium
extension=sodium
 করে দিলে কাজ করবে

2. database migrate করতে হবে
php artisan migrate

3.
 'guards' => [
        'web' => [
            'driver' => 'session',
            'provider' => 'users',
        ],

        'api' => [

            'driver' => 'passport',

            'provider' => 'users',

        ],

php artisan make:controller Api/Auth/AuthController
php artisan make:controller Api/Auth/ForgotPasswordController
